### Status Indicators

**Position Status (Top Right):**
- `âœ“ READY` (green) = In proper push-up position, counting enabled
- `âœ— INVALID POS` (red) = Not in position, counting disabled

**Metrics (Bottom Left):**
- **Elbow**: Current elbow angle
- **Arm-Back**: Arm-to-back parallelism (green [PARALLEL] when good)
- **Knee**: Knee angle (green when straight)

### Warning Messages

